category: KDE Graphics
requires: create calligra-libs libexiv2_11 libfftw3_3 libgcc1 libGL1 libGLEW1.7 libGLU1 libilmbase6 libjpeg8 libkdecore5 libkdcraw20 liblcms2_2 libOpenGTL0.8 libopenjpeg1 libpng14 libpoppler-qt4_3 libQtCore4 libQtGTL0.1 libQtGui4 libQtOpenGL4 libQtSvg4 libQtXml4 libstdc++6 libtiff5 libX11_6
external-source: calligra
sdesc: "KDE layered pixel image editing program"
ldesc: "Krita is a painting and image editing application for Calligra Suite. 
Krita contains both ease-of-use and fun features like guided painting 
(never before has it been so easy to airbrush a straight line!) and 
high-end features like support for 16 bit images, CMYK, L*a*b and even 
OpenEXR HDR images."
